    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>###基本语法</p><blockquote><p>this is my first blog practice</p></blockquote><p>that was a 引用<br>this is a 列表<br>无序列表：减号加空格</p><ul><li>无序列表<br>有序列表：</li></ul><ol><li>有序列表</li><li>2</li><li>3</li></ol><p>! <a href="https://image.baidu.com/search/detail?ct=503316480&amp;z=0&amp;ipn=d&amp;word=%E5%90%89%E4%BB%96%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87&amp;hs=2&amp;pn=2&amp;spn=0&amp;di=134712095430&amp;pi=0&amp;rn=1&amp;tn=baiduimagedetail&amp;is=0%2C0&amp;ie=utf-8&amp;oe=utf-8&amp;cl=2&amp;lm=-1&amp;cs=3240904048%2C766823601&amp;os=4123739319%2C2284284364&amp;simid=3437040322%2C385125638&amp;adpicid=0&amp;lpn=0&amp;ln=30&amp;fr=ala&amp;fm=&amp;sme=&amp;cg=&amp;bdtype=0&amp;oriquery=%E5%90%89%E4%BB%96%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87&amp;objurl=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.58pic.com%2F58pic%2F15%2F25%2F10%2F74h58PICe82_1024.jpg&amp;fromurl=ippr_z2C%24qAzdH3FAzdH3Fooo_z%26e3Bcbrtv_z%26e3Bv54AzdH3Frf1AzdH3F8cdc8a09_z%26e3Bip4s&amp;gsm=0&amp;islist=&amp;querylist=" target="_blank" rel="noopener">吉他</a><br>超链接文本：<br><a href="www.baidu.com">baidu</a></p><p><strong>文字加粗</strong>    使用双星号*<em>标记</em>斜体<em>    一个</em>为斜体<br>字体颜色和字体字号使用HTML标签修改：</p><font face="微软雅黑 " color="red" size="28"><p align="center">微软雅黑红色28号居中</p></font>]]></content>
    
